{"tid":364574,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"“微胖”橋本環奈Cosplay主持《海賊王》節目","createTime":"2017-08-18T13:40:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T13:39:29.000Z","uid":55628,"like":15,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"123c74f144128157573d92280394abadcedf425a","tid":364574,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T13:40:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/18/213456_cfea0d7f122961d6059729e6dd7516b6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F18%2F213456_cfea0d7f122961d6059729e6dd7516b6.jpg&h=6cb51b60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&uarr;橋本穿這條裙子仍然能看出很多肉。<br />\n<br />\n原來富士電視有個角色扮演專門節目叫《CosCosPlayPlay》，今年已經是第3次舉辦《One Piece》特備節目，每次都會找明星玩Cosplay，名為《Episode of 東之海Special》。而嘉賓橋本環奈其實是扮演玩具王國篇中的小人送公主蔓雪莉姬！原版是個手掌心大小的Q版金髮可愛女孩，橋本環奈最近有點少肥，cos這角色真是剛剛好。至於她會否在節目內再扮其他角色？節目將在日本時候8月19日凌晨3時50分播出，到時就知道了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/18/213630_0f56acb37db1af380f07456fb2010347.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F18%2F213630_0f56acb37db1af380f07456fb2010347.jpg&h=bc9911e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&uarr;橋「胖」還模仿羅的手勢。<br />\n<br />\n來源：<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E7%8E%A9%E7%89%A9/113052/%E5%BE%AE%E8%83%96%E6%A9%8B%E6%9C%AC%E7%92%B0%E5%A5%88Cosplay%E4%B8%BB%E6%8C%81-%E6%B5%B7%E8%B3%8A%E7%8E%8B-%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%258A%2580%25E7%258E%25A9%25E7%2589%25A9%2F113052%2F%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E8%2583%2596%25E6%25A9%258B%25E6%259C%25AC%25E7%2592%25B0%25E5%25A5%2588Cosplay%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%258C%2581-%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E8%25B3%258A%25E7%258E%258B-%25E7%25AF%2580%25E7%259B%25AE&d=e8oqb%2FFwxa2VK6eYLlhPaQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=e9cffa9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E7%8E%A9%E7%89%A9/113052/%E5%BE%AE%E8%83%96%E6%A9%8B%E6%9C%AC%E7%92%B0%E5%A5%88Cosplay%E4%B8%BB%E6%8C%81-%E6%B5%B7%E8%B3%8A%E7%8E%8B-%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2f805faf76d3a06d6535763b3a15bb181167707","tid":364574,"uid":37005,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T13:50:14.000Z","msg":"都仲好靚女"},{"pid":"bc1c1ffdaeedf9572caa3dbab3812cfc24481f04","tid":364574,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T14:04:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都仲好靚女</blockquote><br />\n都係，我洗自己腦當佢發育緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d79c2d1a2408bd78db3f66344e4ff02af305989","tid":364574,"uid":5157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T14:07:19.000Z","msg":"BABY FAT!! 一定係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2e143fd21ad0c6750163cfc06ae35997b3b373","tid":364574,"uid":53122,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T14:13:58.000Z","msg":"食避孕丸食到肥晒"},{"pid":"1ecb16dd0d5215bbc2d5a580b5c7631a0c5f1240","tid":364574,"uid":15155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T14:16:30.000Z","msg":"見標題仲諗住會變成點<br />\n結果仲係好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70dcac07c4f58bb500f8cbda0002884e088c4229","tid":364574,"uid":8258,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T14:17:34.000Z","msg":"點解宜家會咁漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n宜家唔做idol冇晒合照event<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6a962f605550f3db367d8b89b85d1758a5e812f","tid":364574,"uid":14497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T14:17:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食避孕丸食到肥晒</blockquote><br />\n對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gi